{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 2078, "height": 2823, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "杜窑村", "block_bbox": [976, 244, 1286, 308], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "杜窑村，今属城关镇塔泥村。相传，在村东南里许老赵沟内，杜氏有窑洞三孔，乃祖上从窑湾、坻坞西村迁来时居住之地，后因义马市扩建地域，窑洞被覆盖。", "block_bbox": [349, 379, 1887, 495], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "杜窑村位于渑池县城东五公里，陇海铁路、310国道北塔泥村北200米。全村有人口500余人，其中杜氏200余口。经祖上十一世、十四世迁来，现已繁衍至二十一世。\n", "block_bbox": [348, 512, 1891, 701], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "渑池杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [176, 739, 258, 1470], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "杜窑村杜氏世系大致分南北院和东西阙二支世系分列如下。", "block_bbox": [439, 716, 1536, 765], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "*南北院支：", "block_bbox": [447, 788, 690, 836], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "流芳公忠—杲——真金——三光—从龙—琨—炳——允霄—廷贵——梦鲛——进怀——建华——清云(十四世而迁杜窑)", "block_bbox": [350, 852, 1889, 974], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 7}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "*东西阙支：", "block_bbox": [450, 995, 686, 1043], "block_id": 7, "block_order": 8}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "流芳公—忠—果—真金—三乐—跃龙—芳—桐—允朋廷琏——云章（十一世而迁杜窑）\n", "block_bbox": [351, 1059, 1886, 1183], "block_id": 8, "block_order": 9}, {"block_label": "number", "block_content": "一二七", "block_bbox": [183, 2143, 237, 2258], "block_id": 9, "block_order": null}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "lab